data.description: A fantastic opportunity for those seeking a fixer-upper with incredible potential. Situated on a generously-sized dividable lot, this property presents an array of possibilities for savvy investors andhomeowners alike. With its dividable lot status, this property offers the unique advantage of being able to be split into separate parcels, providing opportunities for future development or investment ventures. With separately metered water and gas, the home is ready to accommodate a trailer or second home. Whether you're looking for additional living space for extended family members or an income-generating rental unit, thishome expands the possibilities even further.
